Ronke Ojo (amụrụ ya na ụbochi gbara iri na asaa na onwa asaa na afọ 1974) nke amara aha ya bụ Ronke Oshodi Oke bụ onye na-eme ihe nkiri na Nigeria, onye egwu, onye isi na onye na-emepụta ihe nkiri
Ronke bụ agbụrụ Ondo Steeti mana amụrụ ya na Oworonshoki, Lagos State Southwest Nigeria, ebe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ praịmarị na sekọndrị

Ọ malitere ọrụ ya site na otu ihe nkiri akpọrọ Star Parade n'okpuru nduzi nke Fadeyi, onye na-eme ihe nkiri Nigeria ma bụrụ onye a ma ama na afọ 2000 mgbe ọ pụtara na ihe nkiri akpọrọ Oshodi Oke, nke o si nweta aha ọkwa ya
Ọrụ egwu ya malitere na 2014, n'otu afọ ahụ ọ malitere album mbụ ya nke a ga-ewepụta
Na 2015, o weputara otu Ori Mi nke gosiputara 9ice
